{"tid":2063175,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美重手制裁   讓中国科研退回工業時代","createTime":"2020-06-13T16:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T02:05:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"193d846e6bc34df25febf562bd76d6c61351876c","tid":2063175,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/06/13/realtime/8030122.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=465\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F06%2F13%2Frealtime%2F8030122.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D465&h=28448da1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被美國列入制裁黑名單的北京計算科學研究中心，就是研究開發大陸超級電腦「天河二號」的重要推手。新華社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5月26號美國發布對中國33家企業和機構予以制裁，指控它們幫忙中共官方監視新疆維族，或涉及大規模毀滅性武器和其他軍事活動。其中哈爾濱工業大學和哈爾濱工程大學赫然在列，學校為何被列為制裁名單，是因這兩所學校被稱為大陸軍事和科研重鎮。<br />\n<br />\n哈爾濱工業大學（哈工大）是中共國防七大院校之一，連大學社團都和中共國防有關，是中共戰機和航天工程研究重鎮。它的王牌科系有：飛行器設計與工程、材料科學與工程、建築學、機械、計算機等。至於哈爾濱工程大學，其前身是大陸第一所高等軍事技術學府「中共解放軍軍事工程學院」（俗稱「哈軍工」）...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120883/4634227\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120883%2F4634227&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJhUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=ff731c83\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120883/4634227</a>"},{"pid":"8bda9db84083012663bedf5ea424053e8bdb823a","tid":2063175,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T17:12:45.000Z","msg":"侵侵：哈，軍工！收皮！"},{"pid":"376a132a969bbc4e8e5a2bb46a94b0486d3978a2","tid":2063175,"uid":246446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T17:17:01.000Z","msg":"石器時代"},{"pid":"986299653f3f0f6d552cb1f3d424600cb2d1eba5","tid":2063175,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T17:19:00.